  <section style="padding: 3rem 0;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px; line-height: 1.9;">
      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you use the bill checker tool on PakistanBill.online, your reference number or account number is sent to the relevant government portal (PITC, ke.com.pk, sngpl.com.pk, etc.) to retrieve your bill. <strong>We do not store any reference numbers, account numbers, or bill data on our servers.</strong> The request goes directly from your browser to the official portal via our proxy, and the response is displayed to you only.</p>
      <p>We collect anonymized usage analytics (page views, device type, country) through Google Analytics 4 and Cloudflare Analytics to improve our service. No personally identifiable information is stored in our analytics systems.</p>

      <h2>2. Cookies</h2>
      <p>PakistanBill.online uses minimal cookies for analytics purposes (Google Analytics). These cookies do not contain personally identifiable information. You can disable cookies in your browser settings without affecting your ability to check bills on this website.</p>

      <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
      <p>We do not sell, trade, or share any user data with third parties. Bill data fetched through our tool is not stored on our servers and is never transmitted to any party other than your browser.</p>

      <h2>4. Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p>Some pages on PakistanBill.online link to official government portals (ke.com.pk, sngpl.com.pk, ssgc.com.pk, ptcl.com.pk, etc.). Once you leave our website, you are subject to those portals' own privacy policies. We have no control over their data practices.</p>

      <h2>5. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>PakistanBill.online does not knowingly collect data from children under 13. This website provides utility bill information that is generally intended for adults who are responsible for paying household bills.</p>

      <h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. Continued use of PakistanBill.online after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

      <h2>7. Contact</h2>
      <p>For privacy-related questions, email <a href="mailto:info@pakistanbill.online">info@pakistanbill.online</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
